title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 2 2022

description:
Chinese ambassador responds to Pelosi trip. SCOTUS primed to strike down affirmative action in Harvard case. KJP says Biden brought down gas prices. Radio host Mark Moss talks to Buck about the economy and his new book, "The UnCommunist Manifesto." TV show recommendations pour in for Buck and Carrie.
